org.yamcs.xtceproc

Class XtceTmProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractService
      • org.yamcs.xtceproc.XtceTmProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.common.util.concurrent.Service, YamcsService, ContainerProvider, ParameterProvider, ProcessorService, TmSink, TmProcessor

    public class XtceTmProcessor
extends com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractService
implements TmProcessor, ParameterProvider, ContainerProvider
    Does the job of getting containers and transforming them into parameters which are then sent to the parameter request manager for the distribution to the requesters. Relies on XtceTmExtractor for extracting the parameters out of containers
